 <div class="alert alert-secondary mt-4">
    <span class="oi oi-pencil me-2" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <strong>@Title</strong>

    <ul>
        <li>As manager you can view all pages</li>
        <li>As cashier you can view only view the "Customers" page</li>
        <li>As staff member you can only view the "Items" page
        </li>
